273
0:15:12.083,000 --> 0:15:15,000
In the end, this is all in our responsibility.

274
0:15:15.956,000 --> 0:15:16,000
The new way of business --

275
0:15:17.289,000 --> 0:15:2,000
it's the consumer we report to, not to the corporate boards.

276
0:15:21.019,000 --> 0:15:22,000
You see,

277
0:15:23.16,000 --> 0:15:26,000
if you are right with your people,

278
0:15:27.276,000 --> 0:15:29,000
if you are right with your community,

279
0:15:29.983,000 --> 0:15:31,000
if you are right with your product,

280
0:15:32.634,000 --> 0:15:34,000
you will be more profitable,

281
0:15:34.967,000 --> 0:15:36,000
you will be more innovative,

282
0:15:37.023,000 --> 0:15:39,000
you will have more passionate people working for you

283
0:15:39.555,000 --> 0:15:4,000
and a community that supports you.

284
0:15:41.561,000 --> 0:15:44,000
And that's what the anti-CEO playbook is all about.

285
0:15:47.355,000 --> 0:15:5,000
The treasure that I found in that factory --

286
0:15:55.22,000 --> 0:15:57,000
dignity of work,

287
0:15:57.552,000 --> 0:15:58,000
strength of character,

288
0:15:59.476,000 --> 0:16:,000
human spirit --

289
0:16:01.212,000 --> 0:16:03,000
