290
0:16:07.088,000 --> 0:16:08,000
Brothers and sisters,

291
0:16:09.874,000 --> 0:16:13,000
there are people and places all around the world

292
0:16:16.232,000 --> 0:16:17,000
left out and left behind.

293
0:16:19.193,000 --> 0:16:21,000
But their spirit is still strong.

294
0:16:24.49,000 --> 0:16:25,000
They just want another chance,

295
0:16:26.444,000 --> 0:16:29,000
they want someone to give them a chance again,

296
0:16:29.895,000 --> 0:16:32,000
not to just build it back, but build it better than before.

297
0:16:34.52,000 --> 0:16:38,000
And this is the difference between return on investment

298
0:16:39.362,000 --> 0:16:4,000
and return on kindness.

299
0:16:42.717,000 --> 0:16:46,000
This is the difference between profit

300
0:16:46.789,000 --> 0:16:47,000
and true wealth.

